➜『千家诗词』王宝发诗词精选
http://www.sohu.com/a/415899364_753274	17964
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200901/f77a3faadeb340e5a964e9cbe088fe7b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>王宝发，吉林通化人，六零后，诗词爱好者，中华诗词学会会员。毕业于吉林市四平师范学院地理系。愿将诗情融入生活，让生活蕴含诗意！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>乡村赋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">村庐傍碧溪，叶茂掩莺啼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">野绿弥沟壑，花香漫柳堤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">锄禾怜壮汉，摘豆悯娇妻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汗透清风爽，归来日落西。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>晚秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">霜浓寒乍起，风疾叶纷飞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">户御装容厚，蝉鸣力势微。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云衔群雁去，霞伴垛粱归。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老屋垂青袅，残阳透五晖。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冰凌花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二月春光肆意裁，柔姿僻角破冰来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽无国色雍容貌，也学梅花伴雪开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>暮色稻田</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">方池日暮绿连绵，鸟瞰纤秧已落田。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谐律清波苗共舞，蛙声一片说丰年。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
